trans-unit.target: CS2020 de erro do compilador | Documentos do Microsoft

trans-unit.source: Only the first set of input files can build a target other than 'module'
trans-unit.target: Somente o primeiro conjunto de arquivos de entrada pode criar um destino diferente de 'module'

trans-unit.source: In a multi-output compilation, the first output file must be built with [/target:exe](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-exe-compiler-option.md), [/target:winexe](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-winexe-compiler-option.md), or [/target:library](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-library-compiler-option.md).
trans-unit.target: Em uma compilação de várias saída, o primeiro arquivo de saída deve ser criado com [/target: exe](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-exe-compiler-option.md), [/target: winexe](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-winexe-compiler-option.md), ou [/target: Library](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-library-compiler-option.md).

trans-unit.source: Any subsequent output files must be built with [/target:module](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-module-compiler-option.md).
trans-unit.target: Os arquivos de saída subsequentes devem ser criados com [/target: Module](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-module-compiler-option.md).
